--> se arreglo:	
1: /etc/apache2 $ sudo nano apache2.conf
@: Add :servername localhost


Luego 

/etc/init.d $ sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart
[....] Restarting web server: apache2(2)No such file or directory: apache2: could not open error log file /var/log/apache2/error.log.
Unable to open logs
Action 'start' failed.
The Apache error log may have more information.
 failed!

--> Solucion:

/var/log $ sudo mkdir apache2
/var/log $ cd apache2/
/var/log/apache2 $ sudo touch error.log

/var/log/apache2 $ sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart
[ ok ] Restarting web server: apache2.

!!!Congratulate!!!!!

